<h2 id="section-top">Neurology</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1155">Salford Royal NHS Foundation Trust</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentb48be4c0f6c84164a45309a2e1029ca2">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="young woman" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=41357" style="border-width:0px;"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>We manage patients with a wide variety of Neurological problems including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Parkinson's disease </li>
<li>Epilepsy </li>
<li>Multiple Sclerosis </li>
<li>Headache </li>
<li>Neuromuscular disease</li>
</ul>
<p>Find out more by <a href="http://www.srft.nhs.uk/about-us/depts/">visiting our section on the Salford Royal website</a>.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel name-thingsshouldknowmodule">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Things you should know</h3>
<p>We also work closely with the Stroke Unit and the Neurosurgery Unit.</p>
</div>
</div>
